{"tid":2492262,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"有關血小板減少症嘅疑問","createTime":"2021-04-17T03:46:16.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-17T03:49:56.000Z","uid":358559,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"b9d9ec944c859768e593ba763b9c1b08a06a3afd","tid":2492262,"uid":358559,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T03:46:16.000Z","msg":"平時輕輕撞一撞就會瘀晒,之前仆街鏟落樓梯成隻腳瘀晒<br />\n連腳腕位都有瘀(明明冇撞到嗰度),啲瘀先一個月先散晒仲要啲瘀散完仲會有好淺嘅印<br />\n一受傷就好難止血試過有傷口流血流成四粒鐘都止唔到血<br />\n同埋每次刷親牙都流牙血<br />\n上網搵呢啲症狀血小板減少症同糖尿病有啲似<br />\n有冇人都係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e92f2fee8969900d70657f86b076fc12b8b4825c","tid":2492262,"uid":46192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T03:47:26.000Z","msg":"你有無睇醫生。"},{"pid":"3091d5a6942287488efc85ad7f4a37ef013db6d5","tid":2492262,"uid":354738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T03:48:14.000Z","msg":"如果你認真想知道答案我建議你睇醫生好過上連登"},{"pid":"a75c42aef1a2b3bb5f0b57707d90422a1215162e","tid":2492262,"uid":20429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T03:48:33.000Z","msg":"糖尿腳啦你肥仔"},{"pid":"7973be8c0731d2a7c9249ae5e666d3707e51a318","tid":2492262,"uid":39597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T03:49:32.000Z","msg":"我細個試過，醫咗幾年。<br />\n<br />\n發現嗰陣係流鼻血止唔到。<br />\n<br />\n最明顯係手臂/身體其他有紅點，你留意吓。"},{"pid":"d33c6ce9a60501fa473975fe3f67e9d9eaedc0c5","tid":2492262,"uid":181549,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T03:49:56.000Z","msg":"幾多歲？有無抽過血做body check"}]}